# Development Conventions

## TR-GOV-001 — Config/model-string consistency check

scripts/check-config-consistency.py detects retired model strings and drift within an app. Run before merge; CI integration recommended.

## TR-GOV-002 — Deferred-work tagging convention

Tag deferred work as LUMIA-DEBT or POC-EXCEPTION. scripts/debt-report.py compiles tags for maturity checklist reconciliation.

## TR-GOV-003 — Process intensity mode declared per work session

Work sessions may declare a process intensity mode, such as full or poc-fast. Security and agent safety requirements still apply regardless of mode; deferred gates must be recorded as structured debt or POC exceptions.
